# $Id: README,v 1.3 2002/05/01 13:21:00 rowan Exp $

In order to install and use this package you will need Perl version
5.004 or better, mod_perl and Mail::IMAPClient. Installation as usual:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

